Class Name: Skill

Package: (if applicable, e.g., models)
Language: Java

Description:

The Skill class represents a battle ability that a Rooster can use in combat. Each skill has a name, damage value, type, and an associated sound effect. This class provides a simple, immutable structure to store and access skill attributes.

Key Features:

Stores skill name, damage, type, and sound effect.

Immutable class design ensures that skill properties cannot be changed after creation.

Supports multiple skill types (e.g., fire, rock, dark, normal).

Integrates with battle mechanics to calculate damage in combination with Rooster attributes and type effectiveness.


